<html>
	<head>
		<title>Pond/EMail Gateway -- {{.Title}}</title>
		<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=iso-8859-1">
		<meta name="author" content="Bernd Fix <brf@hoi-polloi.org>"></meta>
		<meta name="robots" content="INDEX,FOLLOW"></meta>
		<meta name="revisit-after" Content="20 days"></meta>
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="{{.Root}}pondgw.css"></link>
	</head>
	<body>
    	<ul class="nav">
    		<li><a href="/"        >Home</a></li>
    		<li><a href="/register">Register</a></li>
    		<li><a href="/usage"   >Usage</a></li>
    		<li><a href="/token"   >Token</a></li>
    		<li><a href="/tools"   >Tools</a></li>
    	</ul>
    	<input type="checkbox" id="nav-trigger" class="nav-trigger" />
		<label for="nav-trigger"></label>

		<div class="site-wrap">
		    <div id="header">
		    	<p id="title"><img id="logo" src="images/logo.png"/> &nbsp; Pond/EMail Gateway</p>
		    </div>
		    
			<div class="content">
			    <div class="main">
			    	{{.Content}}
			    </div>
			    <div class="sidebar">
			    	<div class="spacer">
				    	<div class="box">
							<p class="button"><a class="button solid" href="/register">Register</a></p>
							<p><small><b>If you are a Pond user</b> you <u>need</u> to register (and to peer)
							with the gateway to be able to use its services.</small></p>
							<p><small><b>If you are an EMail user</b> you <u>should</u> register at
							the gateway to receive messages encrypted with your GnuPG key.</small></p>
							<p><small>Registration (and the service itself) is free and does <b>not</b>
							require you to reveal <i>who you are</i> or <i>what you are doing</i>.
							We respect the privacy of our users.</small></p>
				    	</div>
			    	</div>
			    </div>
			</div>
			    
		    <div id="footer">
		    	<div class="foot-left">
					<p id="disclaimer"><b>DISCLAIMER</b>: The gateway service may be unavailable or may suffer loss of data
					at any time. Please be patient with us if it fails or delivers unexpected
					results. Nonetheless: please register and use the service so we can
					improve the gateway to serve you all better in the future.</p>
		    	</div>
		    	<div class="foot-right">
		    	</div>
		    	<div class="clear">
		    		<p id="subtitle">&copy; 2014-2015 Bernd Fix &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;Y&lt;</p>
		    	</div>
		    </div>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>